          <title>Left-hander Cole Ragans and Royals agree to $13.25 million, 3-year contract</title>
          <description><![CDATA[SUPRISE, Ariz. (AP) — All-Star left-hander Cole Ragans and the Kansas City Royals agreed Friday to a $13.25 million, three-year contract. Ragans gets a $250,000 signing bonus and salaries of $1 million this year, $4.5 million in 2026 and $7.5 million in 2027.]]></description>
